         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">17/3/95 ¶  ¶ Am quite touched, honored friend, with sending the memorial-medal of your celebrated father. It will be preserved with my best treasures such as the Royal Medal of the R.S. of London, and...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">95.03.17</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">To Casimir de Candolle</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">Bibliothèque des Conservatoire et Jardin botaniques, Geneva.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">17/3/95</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Am quite touched, honored friend, with sending the memorial-medal of your celebrated father. It will be preserved with my best treasures such as the Royal Medal of the R.S. of London, and will be honored also by my heirs, when I shall have passed away! The portrait of your illustrious parent in my study-room reminds me daily of him.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I have some hope, that the lithograms of Candolleaceous plants will soon be continued.<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn0" n="1">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>M's hopes came to nothing, no further Decades of his<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-style: italic; ">Iconography of Candolleaceous plants</seg>
                        <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>were published after the first (B92.13.02).</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>I am now anxious to get the drawings done, so that somewhat later, when funds will become available, quickly the lithography can be proceeded with. My phytographic work had however largely to be laid aside during the last 3 years so that still more time could be devoted to the<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">rural</hi>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>interests in this time of financial depression here.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>The nineth edition of the "Select plants," again considerably augmented will be commenced to be printed next month,<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn1" n="2">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>B95.13.02.</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>so that it can appear still in 1895. With regardful and grateful remembrance</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">your</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ferd. von Mueller.</p>
         </div>
      </body>
